{
  "stem": "12289.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They opened a kind of a-- a possibility there, in the-- in the-- when they encircled Buda.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- they opened a-- a sort of a gate for the Germans, who said, 'we'll try this.' So they tried to evacuate and marched out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The whole army that were in Buda marched out and out of the city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Russians were just waiting for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So when they have got them out, they killed them all by machine guns.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it was an easy matter for the Soviets then to enter the Buda side without any fightings at all.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that-- that saved-- that saved the-- the civilian population in Buda.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- the-- the-- the Nazi, the Hungarian Nazi tried to enter and take away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they managed, in the-- in the very last days, to get out perhaps a couple of hundreds or whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took them to the Danube and shot them and throw them into the Danube.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were grateful that the main part were-- were saved.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The main part in these houses, of the population, who were in these-- in these houses were saved.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was on the Buda side, so I didn't see that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was in-- in February, I think, the beginning of February.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We thought that, why should we-- why should we stay on in Buda, with the Swiss, we and the neutral embassies, and be part of a bloodbath here, when the fighting will start?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have done our share.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- I-- I suggested we try to evacuate the embassies from that part.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As I said, happily enough, that-- this situation never came about, which we have feared.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But anyhow, I-- we tried to evacuate.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
